*Uh* se zima, zato smo već zatvorili prozore. (It's getting cold, so we already closed the windows.)

*Uh* se kola zaustavila, čekali smo da izađe vozač. (The car suddenly stopped, we were waiting for the driver to get out.)

*Uh* mi nismo imali nikog da nam pomogne. (We didn't have anyone to help us.)

*Uh* se učinilo da je bilo bezvezno čekati. (It seemed pointless to wait.)

*Uh* nam je trebalo više vremena da dođemo do cilja. (It took us more time to reach our destination.)